<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.6">
<l>makiḻkoṭ ṭeyva mulōka malōka</l>
<l>makiḻkoḷ cōti malarnta vammāṉē</l>
<l>makiḻkoḷ cintaicol ceykaikoṇ ṭeṉṟu</l>
<l>makiḻvuṟ ṟuṉṉai vaṇaṅka vārāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O father whose joyful light blooms</l>
<l>in the joyful gods, [this] world [and] the immaterial world,</l>
<l>come so that [we] bow to you in joy,</l>
<l>always with joyful thoughts, words [and] acts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
